    <section name="Deployment">
      <p>RSB should deploy fine on any Java web-container supporting Servlet
        2.5.</p>
    </section>
    <section name="Configuration">
      <p>
        RSB is configured with a unique JSON file named
        <b>rsb-configuration.json</b>, which must be located at the root of the JVM classpath.
      </p>
      <subsection name="Samples">
        <p>Here are a few examples of configuration files:</p>
