          </li>
          <li><a href="misc/rsb-configuration-redis.json">Redis statistics store</a>: a minimal configuration with an optional Redis statistics store configured:
           <iframe src="misc/rsb-configuration-redis.json" frameborder="0" scrolling="auto" width="100%" height="200"></iframe>
          </li>
          <li><a href="misc/rsb-configuration-full.json">Full configuration</a>: a complete configuration with examples for all the different job deposit methods:
           <iframe src="misc/rsb-configuration-full.json" frameborder="0" scrolling="auto" width="100%" height="200"></iframe>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <iframe frameborder="0" src="misc/rsb-configuration-minimal.json" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="300" />
